OpenMP 4.0
----------
1. Wait for the second OpenMP 4.0 release candidate (February 2013) and
   have a look at the new error handling features. Evaluate if this
   may be integrated in ParallelPrimeSieve.cpp.
2. Once OpenMP supports array reduction I should use it in
   ParallelPrimeSieve.cpp.
3. Test if the new OpenMP 4.0 affinity() clause speeds up primesieve.
